Hello! Thank you for contacting RT 6 Boozers. My name is Jamie, and I'm here to assist you today.

Hi Jamie! I'm looking for some information about your specials.

Of course! I'd be happy to help with that. May I ask for your name, please?

Sure, my name is Alex.

Thanks, Alex! To better assist you, could you also provide the last four digits of your phone number?

Absolutely, it’s one two three four.

Thank you! Now, could you please tell me your date of birth for our records?

Sure, it's May second, nineteen eighty-five.

Great! Now, regarding our specials, we have happy hour from five to seven PM and two-for-one deals on select drinks.

That sounds wonderful! I might swing by later.

Fantastic! Thank you for your time today, Alex. If you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
